---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Contact Us" description="Get in touch with PlainProcedure. Questions, feedback, or data corrections."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Contact' }]}>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Contact Us</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
      <p>Whether you have spotted a discrepancy in procedure pricing, want to suggest a feature for comparing Medicare costs, or simply have a question about our data sources, we welcome your input.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Email</h2>
      <p>
        The fastest way to reach us is by email:
        <a href="mailto:hello@plainprocedure.com" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">hello@plainprocedure.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Data Corrections</h2>
      <p>If you believe any data displayed on PlainProcedure is inaccurate, please email us with the specific page URL and the correction. We source our data from CMS Medicare Physician & Other Practitioners and CMS Hospital Compare datasets and update regularly.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">About PlainProcedure</h2>
      <p>PlainProcedure is a project by <a href="https://kiznis.studio" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kiznis Studio</a>. We build free, open data tools powered by official government and public datasets.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
